Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.02,0:00:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,适合我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不会很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我下面已经快不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有可能很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.11,0:00:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你很美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直怕不合适
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,夏天跟冬天的活动 我们一定会很成功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,很不想承认
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,只有喜欢动漫的人能穿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,可以做那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.10,0:01:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.11,0:01:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,今天要跟弟弟玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,要回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.03,0:02:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他之前跟他弟弟去海边玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个好姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我们的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.11,0:03:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,天使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,话说那两个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个去看东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,另一个去看演唱会了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,明明有女神在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他一直看我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我很讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:04:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得很烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就过去打了他一拳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他就倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你好帅喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一直拍我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,说的方式也很恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我的话就揍他了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你果然好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你好可爱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好能依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你的身体好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:08:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就是想要你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我也好喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,想摸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,想被你摸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,痒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有点色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就摸胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们知道这那么透吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,只给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们一定都在幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他们一定边幻想你 边打手枪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他们真的很恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这边谁可以摸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你的手指好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哪个比较好？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.39,0:11:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢这个喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.47,0:11:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好湿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好湿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好湿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好湿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好湿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,让我舒服点
