Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.32,0:34:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.32,0:34:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.33,0:34:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,果然好喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.28,0:34:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,下次再多干我一点
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.24,0:35:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,今天休假吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.31,0:35:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,想给你看个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.31,0:35:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.32,0:35:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.39,0:35:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.32,0:35:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.40,0:35:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你会跟弟弟亲亲吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.34,0:35:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到了喔？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.34,0:35:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.28,0:35:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是说你没男朋友吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.31,0:36:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.32,0:36:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.40,0:36:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,会保密的对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.28,0:36:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,如果会保密的话 会再做更多的好事情
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.31,0:37:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,躺下来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.39,0:37:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有亲过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.33,0:37:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.33,0:37:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,被我夺走你的第一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.42,0:38:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你好会亲
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.29,0:38:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.30,0:38:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,可以多吸点 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.31,0:38:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好软
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.25,0:38:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我也帮你吸
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.32,0:38:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.28,0:39:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们再做很棒的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.29,0:39:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你哪里最敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.36,0:39:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,帮你确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.30,0:39:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.31,0:39:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,奶头这么硬
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.38,0:39:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.32,0:39:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.32,0:39:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.26,0:40:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,脱掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.27,0:40:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮你脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.28,0:40:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.35,0:40:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这样比较舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.22,0:40:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,周围就这样了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.30,0:40:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,直接碰
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.37,0:40:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.31,0:40:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.38,0:40:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.32,0:41:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.26,0:41:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这感觉是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.34,0:41:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.34,0:41:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜欢奶头敏感的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.34,0:41:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.29,0:41:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.30,0:41:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.30,0:41:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.32,0:42:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.32,0:42:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我再来帮你点
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.35,0:42:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,可以看你的肉棒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.29,0:42:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.29,0:42:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,让你舒服点
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.37,0:42:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.31,0:43:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.26,0:43:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.33,0:43:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.20,0:43:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.28,0:43:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.28,0:43:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.22,0:43:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.31,0:44:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.25,0:44:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我被舔了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.27,0:44:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.22,0:44:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话会更舒服对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.22,0:44:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.24,0:45:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.31,0:45:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.18,0:45:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,亲亲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.33,0:45:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你的肉棒好硬喔
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.21,0:45:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,想看我的小穴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.22,0:45:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,想
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.22,0:46:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.24,0:46:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这样看的话我会很害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.25,0:46:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,多看点
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.26,0:46:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你的小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.20,0:46:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,可以摸的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.27,0:46:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.15,0:47:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那边好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.29,0:47:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,会进去
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.24,0:47:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴如何
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.18,0:47:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,很热
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.18,0:47:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这样动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.25,0:47:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,会高潮的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.27,0:47:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,会去
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.21,0:48:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.22,0:48:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好多汁跑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.29,0:48:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我舔
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.29,0:48:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,多舔点
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.23,0:48:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.30,0:48:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.18,0:48:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.19,0:48:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你的舌头好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.26,0:49:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.27,0:49:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,多舔一点
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.29,0:49:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.29,0:49:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.30,0:49:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那边
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.23,0:49:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.24,0:49:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.19,0:49:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好湿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.19,0:50:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.20,0:50:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.20,0:50:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.20,0:50:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,躺下
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.27,0:50:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,想要你的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.22,0:50:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,放了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.22,0:50:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.22,0:50:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.16,0:50:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.30,0:50:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好里面
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.31,0:50:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.25,0:50:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.26,0:51:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我也好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.20,0:51:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好里面
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.20,0:51:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.27,0:51:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.28,0:51:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.29,0:51:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,来了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.16,0:51:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.23,0:51:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.24,0:51:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.24,0:51:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你也多积极点
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.26,0:52:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.20,0:52:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,多干我一点
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.21,0:52:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.28,0:52:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.15,0:52:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.30,0:52:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.30,0:52:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,多亲我一点
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.18,0:53:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.32,0:53:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.33,0:53:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.20,0:53:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你的肉棒插进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.28,0:53:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.29,0:53:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.24,0:54:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,插到好里面
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.26,0:54:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.20,0:54:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.20,0:54:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.28,0:54:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那边
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.21,0:54:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.24,0:55:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,又去了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.17,0:55:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.18,0:55:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬喔
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.26,0:55:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,放进来
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.20,0:55:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好里面
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.22,0:56:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,多干我一点
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.30,0:56:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.30,0:56:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.25,0:56:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,看得到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.26,0:56:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫荡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.27,0:56:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,大力点插进来
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.15,0:57:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.22,0:57:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.17,0:57:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,变的好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.26,0:57:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你再多享受点没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.34,0:58:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.29,0:58:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住的话 想射哪就射哪 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.23,0:58:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.18,0:58:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,多射一点
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.19,0:58:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.27,0:59:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这边吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.27,0:59:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,对 那边
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.22,0:59:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.29,0:59:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,想要被射在嘴巴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.23,0:59:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,多射一点
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.23,0:59:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.17,0:59:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.25,0:59:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.27,1:00:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,射了好多啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.28,1:00:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,会保密对吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.22,1:00:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.24,1:00:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.32,1:01:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,最近都没看到他耶
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.26,1:01:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,之后会很忙的说
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.27,1:01:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他到底在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.27,1:01:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我只要女神幸福就好
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.22,1:01:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.22,1:01:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.29,1:01:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,有写东西
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.30,1:01:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,要去旅行了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.30,1:01:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,已经无法相信人类了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.24,1:01:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不用找我
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.25,1:02:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.25,1:02:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.26,1:02:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.20,1:02:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不看？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.20,1:02:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,看？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.27,1:02:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.26,1:03:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫我别再看了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.27,1:03:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,被他骗了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.16,1:04:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.23,1:04:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你们好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.24,1:04:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,舔肉棒的女生别说话
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.18,1:04:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.18,1:04:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这么相信你
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.19,1:04:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.19,1:04:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.33,1:04:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,处女膜都没声音了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.27,1:04:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我生气了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.28,1:04:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.28,1:04:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,拒绝
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.18,1:05:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.25,1:05:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这什么声音
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.19,1:05:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.26,1:05:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.34,1:05:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这么白的内裤
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.27,1:05:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是不会被骗的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.21,1:05:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,再也不会被骗的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.29,1:06:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.30,1:06:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.30,1:06:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,什么不行？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.24,1:06:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,明明很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.25,1:06:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那边不行
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.25,1:06:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这边吗
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.19,1:06:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,之前也发出过吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.26,1:06:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,每次对吧
